ovic was jubilant as he scored the final tie-break point.Each point needed to be perfect.\", \"from\": 16564, \"to\": 16657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic and Alcaraz were both on the top of their games during the match.\", \"from\": 16658, \"to\": 16732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16671, \"end\": 16678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.013145699441707e-16, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each volley had to be just out of the reach of the other player for a winner.\", \"from\": 16733, \"to\": 16810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic and Alcaraz slid across the court several times, played through the incredible Parisian heat to come through.\", \"from\": 16812, \"to\": 16930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16812, \"end\": 16820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9977203521001445, \"rank\": 0.0022848565682863408, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 16825, \"end\": 16832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1647862603273307e-14, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serbian star was in tears as he held up his country's flag to those at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 16932, \"to\": 17021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16936, \"end\": 16943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9822065077764631, \"rank\": 0.01751244776181644, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic had not won a tournament all year long.\", \"from\": 17023, \"to\": 17071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He exited the French Open due to an injury.\", \"from\": 17072, \"to\": 17115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He played through to reach the Wimbledon final last month but lost to Alcaraz for the second straight season.\", \"from\": 17116, \"to\": 17225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17186, \"end\": 17193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1647862603273307e-14, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Djokovic can all himself an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 17227, \"to\": 17277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17232, \"end\": 17240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9977203521001445, \"rank\": 0.0022848565682863408, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Austen Jewell Smith added to Team USA's medal count on Sunday with a bronze-medal finish in women's skeet shooting.\", \"from\": 17281, \"to\": 17396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith scored a 45 in the final, finishing behind Chile's Francisca Crovetto Chadid and Great Britain's Amber Jo Rutter.\", \"from\": 17398, \"to\": 17517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17447, \"end\": 17452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991708316280519, \"rank\": 0.0008178022664297527, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \