4573905411113e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 17867, \"end\": 17875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure was on.\", \"from\": 17979, \"to\": 17999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee swung herself back and forth on the bars in a solid performance on the apparatus.\", \"from\": 18001, \"to\": 18086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18001, \"end\": 18004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9968382204548635, \"rank\": 0.00310892622195813, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She nearly stuck the landing, hugged her Olympic colleagues and then awaited her scores.She got a 14.800 and wrapped up a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 18087, \"to\": 18222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her sixth Olympic medal and tied with Aly Raisman for third most for an American female gymnast.\", \"from\": 18224, \"to\": 18327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18269, \"end\": 18280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aly Raisman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aly_Raisman\"}, {\"begin\": 18303, \"end\": 18311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999079221852699, \"rank\": 7.964879079912504e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algerian Kaylia Nemour stunned the crowd with an incredible performance.\", \"from\": 18329, \"to\": 18401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She scored a 15.700 on the uneven bars to top the score set by China's Qiu Qiyuan.\", \"from\": 18402, \"to\": 18484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18465, \"end\": 18470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9883318733437247, \"rank\": 0.010501190725310746, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qiu put together an epic performance as well, scoring a 15.500.Nemour got the gold and Qiu got the silver.\", \"from\": 18486, \"to\": 18592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brady Ellison captured a silver medal in men's archery on Sunday at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 18596, \"to\": 18682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18596, \"end\": 18609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Ellison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brady Ellison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Ellison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brady_Ellison\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ellison lost the gold-medal match to South Korea's Kim Woo-jin, 6-5, on a tiebreaker.\", \"from\": 18684, \"to\": 18769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18721, \"end\": 18732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.5796056856395028, \"rank\": 0.6814169235933458, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 18735, \"end\": 18746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Woo-jin_(archer)\", \"score\": 0.9999945822827488, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Woo-jin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Woo-jin_(archer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Woo-jin_(archer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the second medal for Ellison at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 18770, \"to\": 18826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won bronze in the mixed team final with Casey Kaufhold.\", \"from\": 18827, \"to\": 18885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18870, \"end\": 18884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Kaufhold\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Kaufhold\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Kaufhold\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Kaufhold\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ellison has five medals in his Olympic career.\", \"from\": 18887, \"to\": 18933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He won silver in the team event at the 2012 Olympics in London and the 2016 Olympics in Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 18934, \"to\": 19037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18990, \"end\": 18996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9995086102733608, \"rank\": 0.0004906170241929809, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 19022, \"end\": 19036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999804459, \"rank\": 1.9502368908584133e-11, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also scored a bronze in men's final at the 2016 Games as well.\", \"from\": 19038, \"to\": 19103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim has three gold medals at the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 19105, \"to\": 19156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19105, \"end\": 19108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.999371077820992, \"rank\": 0.0005231926506879109, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 19150, \"end\": 19155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999587845942652, \"rank\": 4.121710330413691e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won in team and mixed team earlier in the Games.\", \"from\": 19157, \"to\": 19208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also won gold in the team event in 2016 in Rio and 2021 in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 19209, \"to\": 19277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19255, \"end\": 19258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9884495494083958, \"rank\": 0.011685422467470678, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 19271, \"end\": 19276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9743557114729199, \"rank\": 0.026314419868448936, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea took home the bronze medal as well.\", \"from\": 19279, \"to\": 19326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19279, \"end\": 19290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.7896009882138394, \"rank\": 0.23155891503271886, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee Wooseok topped Germany's Florian Unruh, 6-0.\", \"from\": 19327, \"to\": 19375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19327, \"end\": 19330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9334362528837523, \"rank\": 0.06292026774966743, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 19331, \"end\": 19338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wooseok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wooseok\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wooseok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wooseok\"}, {\"begin\": 19346, \"end\": 19353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8547600818280987, \"rank\": 0.16259439409222912, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 19356, \"end\": 19363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\", \"score\": 0.9836897189463886, \"rank\": 0.016580679253723203, \"text\": \"Florian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic legend Carl Lewis talkedto Fox News Digitalon Saturday and talked about Noah Lyles and the need for him to dominate at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 19379, \"to\": 19525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19394, \"end\": 19404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}, {\"begin\": 19414, \"end\": 19422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9888222971533713, \"rank\": 0.010467028366529603, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 19459, \"end\": 19469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the sport needs someone like him that's a champion.\", \"from\": 19527, \"to\": 19587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's the defending champion, the fastest man in the world right now, and we need someone to grab onto.\", \"from\": 19588, \"to\": 19690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think he's the perfect guy to do that, and I am excited about that,\\\" Lewis said in a recent interview.\", \"from\": 19691, \"to\": 19795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19762, \"end\": 19767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\", \"score\": 0.9371971622632399, \"rank\": 0.0667726233981725, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Lewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think track does better when we do have a superstar.\", \"from\": 19797, \"to\": 19852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why I think if Noah were to win, he would elevate the sport as well.\", \"from\": 19853, \"to\": 19928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19875, \"end\": 19879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.4923526427859438, \"rank\": 0.608922125866371, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Bennet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As opposed to saying 'I wonder who's going to win,' people want to say 'I want him' or 'I do not want him.'\", \"from\": 19929, \"to\": 20036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They want to root for someone, or root against someone.\", \"from\": 20037, \"to\": 20092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it creates more intensity when you have someone that dominates, and that's been throughout history.\", \"from\": 20093, \"to\": 20200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 People have really gravitated to the sport when people really dominated more.\\\"\", \"from\": 20201, \"to\": 20281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles will likely be competing in the 100-meter men's final later today.\", \"from\": 20283, \"to\": 20355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox News' Ryan Morik contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 20357, \"to\": 20405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20357, \"end\": 20365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999927555781843, \"rank\": 5.790841385686335e-06, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 20367, \"end\": 20371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999497465927585, \"rank\": 4.728649169315572e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Sudan suffered a loss inOlympic men's basketballat the hands of Serbia, 96-85, on Saturday and head coach Royal Ivey was upset with the officiating.\", \"from\": 20409, \"to\": 20563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20479, \"end\": 20485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.5799228924277668, \"rank\": 0.7086304315337352, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 20521, \"end\": 20531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Ivey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Ivey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ivey said the foul discrepancy during the game was evidence of bias in the game.\", \"from\": 20565, \"to\": 20645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They shot 31 free throws; we shot six free throws?\\\"\", \"from\": 20645, \"to\": 20697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ivey said.\", \"from\": 20698, \"to\": 20708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us tell the story.\", \"from\": 20709, \"to\": 20732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us tell the real story, because that's a travesty.\", \"from\": 20733, \"to\": 20787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How do they shoot 31 free throws and we shoot six free throws?\", \"from\": 20788, \"to\": 20850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How?\\\"\", \"from\": 20851, \"to\": 20856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Sudan failed to make the knockout round because of the loss.\", \"from\": 20858, \"to\": 20924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My guys were out there giving their all -- blood, sweat and tears -- and you tell me how we shot six free throws?\", \"from\": 20926, \"to\": 21040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We shot one free throw in the second half,\\\" Ivey added.\", \"from\": 21041, \"to\": 21096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Luol Deng, federation president and former NBA star, questioned why there were no African referees at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 21098, \"to\": 21213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21098, \"end\": 21107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luol Deng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luol_Deng\"}, {\"begin\": 21141, \"end\": 21144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999988425543, \"rank\": 1.153977118602674e-09, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know why there is no African referees in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 21215, \"to\": 21279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's 2024,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 21280, \"to\": 21300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we are representing the continent, then we have got to be represented fully.\", \"from\": 21301, \"to\": 21381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something that we have got to keep working on.\", \"from\": 21382, \"to\": 21435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if these referees are not familiar with our game, with our style, then I do not know what the world championship or the Olympics is.\", \"from\": 21436, \"to\": 21572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it just a European basketball style and we are not allowed to be aggressive?\\\"\", \"from\": 21573, \"to\": 21653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 21655, \"to\": 21703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21659, \"end\": 21675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9985917172835389, \"rank\": 0.001410252270517684, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anthony Edwards emerged as a legitimate NBA star for the Minnesota Timberwolves over the course of the 2023-24 season and helped the team get to the conference finals.\", \"from\": 21707, \"to\": 21874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21707, \"end\": 21722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.885284969361026, \"rank\": 0.12666637966909441, \"text\": \"Anthony Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 21747, \"end\": 21750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999988425543, \"rank\": 1.153977118602674e-09, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer, his popularity has certainly risen as he's made a name for himself on the U.S.Olympic men's basketballteam in a pursuit of a gold medal.\", \"from\": 21876, \"to\": 22025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only that, but Edwards has had the luxury of playing with his basketball idol, Kevin Durant.\", \"from\": 22026, \"to\": 22122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22115, \"end\": 22121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 0.9999999359404248, \"rank\": 5.652472655589071e-08, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards turned heads on Saturday with an incredible dunk during the team's 104-83 win over Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 22124, \"to\": 22227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22215, \"end\": 22226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.8767049568430031, \"rank\": 0.12573647160866924, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edwards led the way with 26 points in 17 minutes off the bench.\", \"from\": 22228, \"to\": 22291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had already told K after the timeout.\", \"from\": 22293, \"to\": 22333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Like, bruh, if I get a break, like, I am going to windmill it,'\\\" Edwards said.\", \"from\": 22334, \"to\": 22413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wanted to go between your legs, but I ain't tried it in a minute.\", \"from\": 22414, \"to\": 22482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I did not want to embarrass myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 22483, \"to\": 22522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He called playing in the Olympics with Durant and LeBron James on the same floor is 'everything I ever dreamed of.\\\"\", \"from\": 22524, \"to\": 22639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22574, \"end\": 22586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Him and Bron, they are the best two people,\\\" Edwards said.\", \"from\": 22641, \"to\": 22700, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Team players, they always want to see the person next to them shine.\", \"from\": 22701, \"to\": 22770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the same way.\", \"from\": 22771, \"to\": 22789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's perfect.\\\"\", \"from\": 22790, \"to\": 22807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 22809, \"to\": 22857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22813, \"end\": 22829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999458365575629, \"rank\": 5.4154415597765915e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taiwanese Olympic boxer Lin Yu-ting will move onto the semifinals of the 57-kilogram division in women's boxing and guaranteed at least a bronze medal at theParis Games.\", \"from\": 22861, \"to\": 23030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22861, \"end\": 22870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9998847877440716, \"rank\": 6.157022119548018e-05, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\"}, {\"begin\": 22885, \"end\": 22896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin has been one of the two boxers caught up in a gender controversy.\", \"from\": 23032, \"to\": 23101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin defeated Bulgaria's Svetlana Kamenova Staneva via unanimous decision in the quarterfinals.\", \"from\": 23102, \"to\": 23196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23115, \"end\": 23123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"score\": 0.9999360997799199, \"rank\": 6.39041077901005e-05, \"text\": \"Bulgaria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bulgaria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin was knocked down twice but threw a couple of jabs to Staneva's face during the bout.\", \"from\": 23197, \"to\": 23285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin was apparently booed after the contest, according to The Sun.\", \"from\": 23287, \"to\": 23352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin and Algerian boxer Imane Khelif have as faced scrutiny over a disqualification from the 2023 International Boxing Association (IBA) Women's World Championship.\", \"from\": 23354, \"to\": 23517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23362, \"end\": 23370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.7403246517464024, \"rank\": 0.348555819910281, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 23377, \"end\": 23389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 23485, \"end\": 23488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9470260021661863, \"rank\": 0.0459542250297672, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both will now be at least bronze medal winners as there is no other match for losing semifinalists.\", \"from\": 23518, \"to\": 23617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"International Olympic Committee president Thomas Bach defended having Lin and Khelif fight in the women's division on Saturday.\", \"from\": 23619, \"to\": 23746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23619, \"end\": 23650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 23661, \"end\": 23672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What is going on in this context in the social media with all this hate speech, with this aggression and abuse, and fueled by this agenda, is totally unacceptable,\\\" Bach said.\", \"from\": 23748, \"to\": 23924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23914, \"end\": 23918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999400246607124, \"rank\": 5.997893537823235e-05, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin has maintained focus on the possibility of winning goal and has not mentioned the scrutiny.\", \"from\": 23926, \"to\": 24021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United Statesentered Sundaywith 61 medals to their count.\", \"from\": 24025, \"to\": 24086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team has put together a performance at the Paris Olympics that included 14 gold, 24 silver and 23 bronze medals.\", \"from\": 24087, \"to\": 24203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vincent Hancock, Simone Biles, Ryan Crouser, Katie Ledecky and the team of Ryan Murphy, Nic Fink, Gretchen Walsh and Torri Huske all took home gold medals on Saturday.\", \"from\": 24205, \"to\